<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id787598a0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s690h"><num value="690h">§ 690h.</num><heading> “Person” defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in sections 690 to 690i of this title the term “person” includes an individual, partnership, association, or corporation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id787598a1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1928-04-23/ch413/s10">Apr. 23, 1928, ch. 413, § 10</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/45/450">45 Stat. 450</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id787598a2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
