<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id787598a4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section 690i, included within the reference to sections 690 to 690i, was omitted from the Code.</p>
</note>
